---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Cookie Policy | Open Energy Services" 
  description="Cookie policy for Open Energy Services."
>
  <div class="pt-32 pb-24 bg-white min-h-[60vh]">
    <div class="container max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-primary-navy mb-8 tracking-tight">
        Cookie Policy
      </h1>
      <div class="prose prose-slate max-w-none text-slate-600 font-medium">
        <p class="mb-4">Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-GB')}</p>
        <p class="mb-4">
          Our website uses cookies to distinguish you from other users of our website. This helps us to provide you with a good experience when you browse our website and also allows us to improve our site.
        </p>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-navy mt-8 mb-4">What are cookies?</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">A cookie is a small file of letters and numbers that we store on your browser or the hard drive of your computer if you agree. Cookies contain information that is transferred to your computer's hard drive.</p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-navy mt-8 mb-4">How we use them</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">We use strictly necessary cookies to make our site work. We also use analytical/performance cookies to recognise and count the number of visitors and see how visitors move around our site when they are using it.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-navy mt-8 mb-4">Managing cookies</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">You can block cookies by activating the setting on your browser that allows you to refuse the setting of all or some cookies. However, if you use your browser settings to block all cookies (including essential cookies) you may not be able to access all or parts of our site.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>